# Ripgrep Binary Distribution

This directory contains pre-compiled ripgrep binaries for different platforms.

## Directory Structure

The binaries should be organized in subdirectories by architecture and OS:

```
third-party/ripgrep/
├── arm64-darwin/
│   └── rg
├── amd64-darwin/
│   └── rg
├── arm64-linux/
│   └── rg
├── amd64-linux/
│   └── rg
├── amd64-windows/
│   └── rg.exe
└── arm64-windows/
    └── rg.exe
```
